In the interest of "getting those missiles ready to destroy the universe", I have set up this sexy asphalt-colored journal for interested and/or fashionably disinterested parties to request things, including, but not limited to: 1. Drawings of stuff 2. Band flyers 3. T-shirt designs 4. Actual t-shirts, which I will make you pay for 5. Naked pictures of J. Blaine Huffman (lol) 6. Other stuff you might think of 666. Naked pictures of the devil! If you're not into stuff, why not return to econorocket or go read some comix?
